          p 
            | Finding a great house doesn't mean it's zoned for great schools. Each family has different educational needs and finding the right place can make all of the difference. Having lived in many of the major school districts herself, Susan can help you find a wonderful home in the best place for your children. 
        .small-12.medium-6.large-4.columns
          h5 Destination Homes
          p 
            | Upstate South Carolina is surrounded by incredible natural beauty, on display in lakes, mountains and open country. If you're looking for a scenic home or second home, Susan's knowledge of the Upstate's landscape will serve as your guide to finding a gorgeous destination called home. 
